name: Name
description: Full name for an object. Must be one row

name: NC Name
description: Used as a primary identifier for an user together with the email. Must be unique across UMS

name: Description
description: Generic text description. Multiple rows and HTML markup is allowed.

name: User Role
description: SA - Super Admin, OA - Organization Admin, DC - Data Contributor, G-Guest

name: Hash
description: Sha1 hash code based on some unique identifier, which iseither too long to be stored, or is private and must not t o be stored in the database such as password etc.

name: General descriptor
description: Random string with some specific semantic meaning

name: Thumbnail preview
description: Preview based on a hash code and MIME type - requires special handling in UI

name: Database
description: Database table - normally associated with an organization - requires special handling in UI

name: Lang
description: 2 character language code available in multi-language system

name: Organization
description: A Client for the application and possessing its own database and UMS

name: Email
description: Primary email used for communication. We don't verify etc. Used as primary identifier

name: Language
description: Preferred language for the user interface

name: ZIP code
description: Zip code specific for the country

name: Location
description: Existing Web address - generated when uploading the image

name: File name
description: Original file name from the file system from where the image is uploaded

name: Hash
description: Hash code to identify the file in Web storage - randomly generated during upload

name: Width
description: Width of the image when displayed in page

name: Height
description: Height of the image when displayed in page

name: Media object
description: Generic media file such as MP3, MPEG etc. It can be also an image with specific format not supported by the browser

name: Location
description: The Web address generated during upload

name: File name
description: Original file name from the file system from where the image is uploaded

name: Hash
description: Hash code to identify the file in Web storage - randomly generated during upload

name: Inventory No.
description: The identifier of the item in the classification of the owner organization

name: Quantity
description: How many parts there in the item

name: Publish data
description: Flag whether to display item in visitor view

name: Transfer in Visitor Catalog
description: Flag whether to transfer in Visitor Catalog

name: Press and TV
description: Mass media information about the item

name: Internet site
description: Web link of an Internet site relaed with the item

name: Invenroy Manager
description: Person who is physically maintaining items

name: Technical Category
description: Enumeration - technical category for the item

name: Material Technique
description: Enumeration for material technique for the item

name: Mass Media Info
description: Mass media information about the item

name: General articles in magazines and newspapers
description: General articles in magazines and newspapers

name: Literature - Basic Info
description: Literature - Basic Info for the item

name: Name
description: Name of the type of publication
